lead_paragraph: Flummoxed by a rearguard action from Championship leaders Hull City in the FA Cup on Saturday, manager Arsene Wenger knows his Arsenal side must sharpen up for next week's Champions League last-16 clash with Barcelona.

headline.print_headline: Wenger Calls for More Arsenal Efficiency Against Barca
headline.main: Wenger Calls for More Arsenal Efficiency Against Barca
